                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I find Rand unpallatable -just to many basic assumptions that i disagree with.  I put here literature in the same catagory as L Ron Hubbard (Battlefield Earth) and Heinline (sp). And the non fiction, well -thats another story.
<br />

<br />
 That said, even though I heavily disagree with thier basic stance, I still would recomend -I personaly like to read things that I disagree with or things that make me think about why I disagree or agree (or make me examine my own views).
